what you do for your girlfriend.

332
00:22:36,146 --> 00:22:37,147
My mistake.

333
00:22:37,898 --> 00:22:40,400
I'll make sure not to miss good points.

334
00:22:40,734 --> 00:22:42,861
-And be honest.
-Okay. Let's keep it honest.

335
00:22:42,944 --> 00:22:45,280
What is So-min going to do?

336
00:22:45,739 --> 00:22:46,740
What?

337
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:48,408
It's just hard.

338
00:22:49,493 --> 00:22:50,869
No, it's okay.

339
00:22:52,329 --> 00:22:53,789
You've been in this field for quite long.

340
00:22:53,872 --> 00:22:56,374
You can't deal with So-min.

341
